text: The 2016 Chinese Taipei Masters Grand Prix will be the 16th grand prix's badminton tournament of the 2016 BWF Grand Prix Gold and Grand Prix. The tournament will be held at the Hsing Chuang Gymnasium in Taipei City, Chinese Taipei on October 11–16, 2016 and has a total purse of $55,000. ==Men's singles== ===Seeds=== # Hsu Jen-hao (Semifinals) #
